---

---

<section id="team" class="bg-surface-page py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-6 lg:px-16">
    {/* Block 1 — Founder profile */}
    <div class="mb-4 text-center">
      <p
        class="text-brand-500 animate-on-scroll mb-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase"
      >
        Who you're working with
      </p>
      <h2
        class="font-heading text-text-primary animate-on-scroll mb-16 text-3xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl lg:text-[41px]"
      >
        A senior partner, not a staffing agency.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mx-auto grid max-w-4xl items-center gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16"
    >
      <div class="animate-on-scroll flex justify-center">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/team/loren-anderson.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img
            src="/images/team/loren-anderson-opt.jpg"
            alt="Loren Anderson, Founder & President of Innovise Technologies"
            width="320"
            height="320"
            class="border-surface-card h-72 w-72 rounded-xl border-4 object-cover shadow-lg md:h-80 md:w-80"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </picture>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <p
          class="text-brand-500 mb-1 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase"
        >
          Founder &amp; President
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-text-primary mb-6 text-2xl font-semibold">
          Loren Anderson
        </h3>

        <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            When Loren takes on a client, the first conversation isn't about
            code. It's about what your business is trying to accomplish and
            where it's stuck. In 15 years of full-stack development and
            technical leadership, he's learned that the real problem is rarely
            what's in the ticket. He'll push back when something doesn't add up.
            He'd rather ask an uncomfortable question now than build the wrong
            thing for three months.
          </p>
          <p>
            He's led technical direction for high-growth platforms, orchestrated
            complex migrations, and built engineering teams from scratch. He
            brings a pragmatic mindset to every engagement, choosing the
            approach that fits your business, not the most impressive one on
            paper.
          </p>
          <p>
            And if your goal is eventually to build your own internal team?
            He'll help you do that too.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/loren-anderson-85953a13/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-text-tertiary hover:text-brand-500 mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path
              d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Block 2 — Collective team */}
    <div class="border-surface-card mt-20 border-t pt-20">
      <div class="grid items-center gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll order-1 md:order-1">
          <p
            class="text-brand-500 mb-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase"
          >
            When more capacity is needed
          </p>
          <h3
            class="font-heading text-text-primary mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl"
          >
            Seasoned leaders. Engineers extending your team.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Larger projects sometimes need more than one engineer. When that's
            the case, Innovise brings in developers matched to your stack and
            stage. You'll always know who's on your project, what they're
            responsible for, and at what level. Innovise organizes developers to
            be an extension of your team.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-on-scroll order-2 md:order-2">
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <picture>
              <source
                srcset="/images/content/team-flipchart.webp"
                type="image/webp"
              />
              <img
                src="/images/content/team-flipchart.jpg"
                alt="A small team working through a plan at the whiteboard"
                width="800"
                height="533"
                class="h-72 w-full object-cover object-center md:h-80 lg:h-96"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </picture>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
